race.comment: ISLE OF ROSE (6) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (18.14) last time in a NG at Richmond Straight. Form from her last run is proving strong. Should bounce back. MAGIC WYLDE (5) could manage only second last time but ran strong time (22.00) at this track over 388m when beaten 1.5 lengths in a Grade 4. This is tougher but looks a leading chance again. CAWBOURNE SPADE (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Libby Keeping (22.52) in a Grade 5. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expecting another good run. WORIMI STAR (3) is worth consideration after filling a hole last start.
